---
title: Family Favourite Lemon & Oregano Chicken with Chive Butter Sauce and Garlicky Green Beans
description: This Family Favourite Lemon & Oregano Chicken is inspired by the flavours of Greece. An easy chive butter sauce brings extra flavour and is a deliciously simple way to elevate your dinner and try something new.
